Invocation Name: madison guide
des:
Explore Madison, the capitol city of the Dairyland state of United States with the Madison Guide. Get to know the top attractions in Madison and the best things to do while you are here!

Some things you can say:
"Alexa, launch Madison Guide",
"Alexa, tell me about Madison",
"Alexa, tell me about attractions",
"Alexa, tell me the top five things to do",
"Alexa, tell me the local news".

Have fun in Mad Town!
